ers to Gather at Protests, Why Doesn’t He Attend One?</span></h4><div class="Promo-author" data-reactid="313"><!-- react-text: 314 -->Robert Mackey<!-- /react-text --><span class="Promo-date" data-reactid="315"><!-- react-text: 316 --> —<!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 317 --> <!-- /react-text --><span data-reactid="318">Apr. 18</span></span></div></div><div class="Promo-excerpt" data-reactid="319"><!-- react-empty: 320 --></div></div></div></a></div></div><div class="Promo-container" data-reactid="321"><div data-reactid="322"></div><div class="Promo Promo--default Promo--video" data-reactid="323"><a class="Promo-link" href="/2020/04/17/coronavirus-fema-trump-misinformation/" data-reactid="324"><div class="GridRow" data-reactid="325"><div class="Promo-image-container" data-reactid="326"><div class="Promo-image-block" data-reactid="327"><div class="ResponsiveImage Promo-image" style="padding-top:50%;" data-reactid="328"><noscript data-reactid="329"><img src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/ad5bd1f0-e9a4-401c-8bcd-e0abe9180a77/ad5bd1f0-e9a4-401c-8bcd-e0abe9180a77.bin?auto=compress,format&cs=srgb&dpr=2&h=450&w=900&fit=crop&crop=faces%2Cedges&_=16a9b30fed6a542d57356b4d399e4727" alt="null" class="ResponsiveImage-image" height="900" width="1800"></noscript></div></div></div><div class="Promo-text" data-reactid="330"><div class="PromoVideoPlayButton Promo-playButton Promo-playButton--in-title" data-reactid="331"></div><div class="Promo-title-block" data-reactid="332"><h4 class="Promo-title" data-reactid="333"><span class="Promo-title-wrap" data-reactid="334">FEMA’s Coronavirus Rumor Control Webpage Sidesteps Trump’s Lies</span></h4><div class="Promo-author" data-reactid="335"><!-- react-text: 336 -->Nick Turse<!-- /react-text --><span class="Promo-date" data-reactid="337"><!-- react-text: 338 --> —<!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 339 --> <!-- /react-text --><span data-reactid="340">Apr. 17</span></span></div></div><div class="Promo-excerpt" data-reactid="341"><!-- react-empty: 342 --></div></div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="Post-comments Post-comments-ct" data-reactid="343"><a class="Post-open-comments-link Post-open-comments-link--closed" href="/2020/03/31/epa-regulations-air-pollution-coronavirus/?comments=1#comments" id="comments" data-reactid="344"><span class="Icon Icon--Arrow_01_Down icon-TI_Arrow_01_Down" data-reactid="345"></span><!-- react-text: 346 --> <!-- /react-text --><span class="Icon Icon--Comment icon-TI_Comment" data-reactid="347"></span><!-- react-text: 348 --> <!-- /react-text --><span class="PostCommentCount" data-reactid="349">Leave a comment</span></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-reactid="350"><div class="Newsletter" data-reactid="351"><div class="GridContainer" data-reactid="352"><div class="GridRow" data-reactid="353"><div class="Newsletter-wrapper" data-reactid="354"><div class="Newsletter-container Newsletter-container--ready Newsletter-container--disable-submission en" data-reactid="355"><div class="Newsletter-content" data-reactid="356"><div class="Logo" data-reactid="357"><div class="Logo-block" data-reactid="358"><a href="/" data-reactid="359"><span class="Logo-fallback" style="color:#8280FF;" data-reactid="360"><!-- react-text: 361 -->The<!-- /react-text --><br data-reactid="362"/><!-- react-text: 363 -->Intercept_<!-- /react-text --><span data-reactid="364"><br data-reactid="365"/><!-- react-text: 366 --><!-- /react-text --></span></span><svg class="Logo-svg" height="50px" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 140 50" width="140px" data-reactid="367"><g data-reactid="368"><path class="Logo-path" d="M51.731,30.458c1.246,0,2.264,1.425,2.264,3.206l-4.605,0.56C49.517,31.781,50.28,30.458,51.731,30.458 M40.789,8.601 c1.247,0,2.265,1.424,2.265,3.206l-4.606,0.559C38.575,9.924,39.339,8.601,40.789,8.601 M92.774,30.458 c1.247,0,2.264,1.425,2.264,3.206l-4.605,0.56C90.56,31.781,91.323,30.458,92.774,30.458 M128.295,46.463H140v-2.188h-11.705 V46.463z M106.642,31.679c0.2